article_title: Photos: Wisconsin volunteers pack food to send to Ebola-stricken Liberia
article_text: The paper, which was published Wednesday in the Mayo Clinic Proceedings, says there is no solid proof that some drugs approved by the U.S. Food and Drug Administration are helping patients live longer.
